	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have the game The Firemen for the SFC.  There was also a version released in EUR in English.  I know it is possible to take the PAL rom and put it on a NTSC cart, but will it run properly?  Is there anything more I'd need to do to the rom first?
<br />
<br />Thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
